<div class="span_2_of_2"><div class="covidbannerfull"><img class="allinlogo" src="https://asset2.cxnmarksandspencer.com/is/image/mands/allinthisto.png?fmt=png-alpha&amp;wid=1920"><h3 class="deliveroo_title">Delicious M&amp;S food and drink to your doorstep</h3>
    <p>We&#39;ve partnered with food delivery company Deliveroo to help give our customers access to essential groceries and some of their M&amp;S favourites and treats. This new service is available across selected M&amp;S stores and in over 100 BP M&amp;S stores – it&#39;s just one of the many ways we are supporting our customers and communities during these unprecedented times&nbsp;</p>
    <p class="allthis">#allinthistogether</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container"><div class="howitworks"><h2>How it works</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="firstRow"><div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground"><img class="deliveroo_img" alt="delivroo_image" src="https://asset2.cxnmarksandspencer.com/is/image/mands/Deliveroo_logo.png?fmt=png-alpha&amp;wid=501"></div>
    <div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground1"><div class="CopyCenter getTheApp"><h3>1. Get the app</h3>
    <p>Download the Deliveroo app via the App Store or Google Play Store. Alternatively, visit deliveroo.co.uk</p>
    <img class="deliveroo_app_size" alt="googleplay" src="https://asset2.cxnmarksandspencer.com/is/image/mands/deliveroo_Ap_logos.png?fmt=png-alpha&amp;wid=438"></div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="secondRow"><div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground2"><div class="copyL"><h3>2. Find your nearest store</h3>
    <p>Enter your delivery address to find an M&amp;S store close to you or search for M&amp;S in the search bar and select the store</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground3"><div class="copyblockk">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
    </div>


    <div class="thirdRow">
        
            <div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground5"><div class="copyL"><h3>3. Time to shop</h3>
                <p>Browse the available range and add to your basket. Check your order by tapping &#39;View Basket&#39;. Then tap &#39;Go to Checkout&#39;, enter your address and pay</p>
                </div>
                </div>
        <div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground4"><div class="copyblockk">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
    


    </div>



    <div class="fourthRow"><div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground6"><div class="copyL"><h3>4. Contact-free delivery</h3>
    <p>All that&#39;s left to do is wait for you order to arrive – you can track its progress via the app. Your health and wellbeing is our top priority, so all customers will be offered contact-free delivery</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col span_1_of_2 brandBackground7"><div class="copyblockk">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
    </div>
