    <p>If you live within the catchment area of one of the 100+ BP M&amp;S stores offering delivery, or any of the below M&amp;S stores, you will be able to get everything from milk and bread to pizza and wine straight to your doorstep. See the full store list <a href="https://asset1.cxnmarksandspencer.com/is/content/mands/Deliveroo_Store_List_FULL_230420-versionpdf.pdf">here</a></p>
